#. type: Content of: <div><p>
msgid "You are running a testing version of Tails. Thanks!"
msgstr "Sie verwenden eine Testversion von Tails. Danke!"

#. type: Content of: <div><ul><li>
msgid "Release candidates are safe to use but might have other problems."
msgstr ""
"Release Candidates sind sicher in der Anwendung, können aber andere Probleme "
"haben."

#. type: Content of: <div><ul><li>
msgid "Beta versions are unsafe to use. Only use beta versions for testing."
msgstr ""
"Beta-Versionen sind unsicher in der Anwendung. Verwenden Sie Beta-Versionen "
"nur zum Testen."

#. type: Content of: <div><p>
msgid ""
"Report any problems to <a href=\"mailto:tails-testers@boum.org\">tails-"
"testers@boum.org</a>."
msgstr ""
"Melden Sie etwaige Probleme an <a href=\"mailto:tails-"
"testers@boum.org\">tails-testers@boum.org</a>."

#. type: Content of: <h1>
msgid "Current calls for testing"
msgstr "Aktuelle Aufforderungen zu Tests"

#. type: Content of: <p>
msgid "None at this moment"
msgstr "Im Moment keine"

#. type: Content of: <h1>
msgid "Other news"
msgstr "Andere Neuigkeiten"

